&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nv">QEMUOPTS&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">+=&lt;/span> -device virtio-blk-device,drive&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>x0,bus&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>virtio-mmio-bus.0
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nf">qemu&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span> $&lt;span class="n">K&lt;/span>/&lt;span class="n">kernel&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">fs&lt;/span>.&lt;span class="n">img&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="err"> &lt;/span> &lt;span class="err"> &lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">$(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nv">QEMU&lt;/span>&lt;span class="k">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">$(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nv">QEMUOPTS&lt;/span>&lt;span class="k">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>这里真正启动了qemu程序，系统的内核、文件系统都在QEMUOPTS中指定。而我们的用户态程序都位于fs.img内：&lt;/p>
